程序包org.springframework.cglib的说明

Spring's repackaging of CGLIB (for internal use only).

This repackaging technique avoids any potential conflicts with dependencies on CGLIB at the application level or from third-party libraries and frameworks.

As this repackaging happens at the class file level, sources and javadocs are not available here.
